text: Cristóbal Merlos is an archer from El Salvador. He was born on 13 November 1978. Merlos competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics.Cristobal Antonio MERLOSCristóbal Merlos == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Salvadoran people Category:Archers Category:Olympians
